  "description": "adds more vanilla style structures to the game",
  "body": "<h1>Explorations</h1>\n<h4>adds more vanilla style structures to the game</h4>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/v31Shw5/divider-red.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\n<p><b>currently added structures:</b></p>\n\n<table>\n    <tbody>\n        <tr>\n            <td><b>Forgotten Well</b></td>\n            <td><b>Jungle Temple</b></td>\n            <td><b>Shrine</b></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/cLxYjbk/forgotten-well.png\" alt=\"forgotten well\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" />\n            </td>\n            <td><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/tY40Ttq/jungle-temple.png\" alt=\"jungle temple\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\" />\n            </td>\n            <td><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/5xKMs5S/shrine.png\" alt=\"shrine\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\"></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td colspan=\"3\"><b>Underground Temple</b></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td colspan=\"3\">\n                <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/0cKmPqp/underground-temple.png\" alt=\"underground temple\" width=\"250\"\n                    height=\"250\" />\n                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n                <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/3SLhq9h/underground-temple-2.png\" alt=\"underground temple\" width=\"250\"\n                    height=\"250\" />\n                &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n                <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/3CfqXrz/underground-temple-3.png\" alt=\"underground temple\" width=\"250\"\n                    height=\"250\" />\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td><b>Floating Island</b></td>\n            <td><b>Large Oak Tree</b></td>\n            <td><b>Logs</b></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LYMX3kg/floating-island.png\" alt=\"floating island\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\">\n            </td>\n            <td><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/9c8YJKD/large-oak-tree.png\" alt=\"large oak tree\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\">\n            </td>\n            <td><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/chKJKLd/logs.png\" alt=\"logs\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\"></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td><b>Desert Ruin</b></td>\n            <td colspan=\"2\"><b>Slime Cave</b></td>\n        </tr>\n        <tr>\n            <td><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/wKZ2wnL/desert-ruin.gif\" alt=\"desert ruin\" width=\"250\" height=\"250\"></td>\n            <td colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/DC7fFYN/slime-cave-raw.png\" alt=\"slime cave\" width=\"500\" height=\"250\">\n        </tr>\n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/v31Shw5/divider-red.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n<p><span>official Datapacks:</span></p>\n<ul>\n    <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/no-more-floating-islands\">NoMoreFloatingIslands</a>\n        => prevents the Floating Islands from generating</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/v31Shw5/divider-red.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\nif you have any questions about the mod, or you want a few insights about upcoming features:\n<br>\nfeel free to join the Discord &nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VQ66pHN/Discord.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"166\" height=\"32\" />\n</a>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">link</a>",
